Police and Judiciary officials in Rongo have destroyed bhang worth Sh2 million.
 The bhang haul which was set a blaze on Friday, had been recovered from over 200 traffickers along Isebania-Kisii road. 
 ALSO READ:

Trigger-happy police officers should be held accountable

 Principal Magistrate Raymon Langat said the decision to destroy the cannabis sativa was to send a powerful message to persons notorious for trafficking drugs.
 “We are sending a message to peddlers and suppliers who are still out  there  that their days are numbered,” Langat said.




